-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Limit
   ->  Sort
         Sort Key: sum((sum(remote_scan.revenue))) DESC
         ->  HashAggregate
               Group Key: remote_scan.worker_column_2, remote_scan.worker_column_3, remote_scan.worker_column_4
